label: Irish Volunteers Memorial Meeting
description: This pamphlet, commemorating memorial meetings in October and November, 1877, includes speeches and histories of the Irish Volunteers Company.  Of special interest, on pages 36-38, are several rolls of the company in service to the Confederacy.  39p.
